genresAdvancedInfo.name: rap gaucho
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Originating in the southern region of Brazil, Rap Gaucho is a subgenre of Brazilian hip-hop that incorporates elements of traditional folk music from the Rio Grande do Sul state. The lyrics often focus on the struggles of the working class and the rural lifestyle of the gauchos, the cowboys of the region.
